smaller companies," says Mr. Ruskin. Such services will
include providing equity capital, strategic financial and
operational advice as well as traditional investment-banking
services.
   The partnership, one of the many boutiques being formed by
former Wall Street executives, also will assist public
companies in divestiture efforts.
