   -- ELECT. COMPONENTS
                                                                                                       

                              1st Qtr.    1st Qtr.     %
   7 Firms                      1990        1989      Chg
                                                                                                       

   AMP Inc                     79,833      77,297     +  3
   Emerson Electric           156,200     147,800     +  6
   Grainger (W.W.)             28,851      27,561     +  5
